### Category 1 — Hard Evals (Must Pass or Score = 0)

**TC1 — Schema compliance, vague query**
```
Input: [{"role": "user", "content": "I need an assessment"}]
Must: recommendations = [], end_of_conversation = false
Must NOT: recommendations with items, crash, missing keys
```

**TC2 — Schema compliance, recommendation turn**
```
Input: enough context to recommend
Must: every item has name + url + test_type, 1-10 items
Must NOT: null recommendations, more than 10 items
```

**TC3 — URLs from catalog only**
```
After any recommendation response:
Must: every url in recommendations exists verbatim in catalog JSON
Must NOT: any invented, modified, or hallucinated URL
```

**TC4 — Turn cap honored**
```
Send 8 messages back and forth
Must: agent still responds on turn 8, end_of_conversation = true by turn 8
Must NOT: crash, refuse to respond, exceed 8 turns
```

**TC5 — Response always valid JSON**
```
Send 20 different inputs including gibberish, empty strings, very long text
Must: every response is parseable JSON with correct keys
Must NOT: plain text response, markdown code blocks around JSON, missing keys
```

